            "image_icon": "shopify://shop_images/Durability-longevity_icon_2c9a0283-c4ff-46c1-84c9-3566aa2c0a9a.png",
            "text_text": "Despite its recyclability, your Mono Series Minimal Pack is built to last. Its robust textile and durable design reduce the need for replacements, lowering environmental impact over time. all Heimplanet gear, including the Mono Series, comes with a lifetime warranty.",
